def-en: In the context of a data set, having a lot of random noise that limits learning on that data set.
def-ga: I gcomhthéacs tacar sonraí, le an-chuid torann randamach ann a chuireann bac ar fhoghlaim ar an tacar sonraí sin.
notes: Cé go bhfuil an 'torannach' i bhFoclóir Uí Dhuinín, is le brí iomlán ar leith atá sé luaite ann.
